Seven years ago, 9 year old me was getting ready to start the biggest adventure ever; moving across the world to another country where you don't know anyone and you don't speak the language isn't easy. School was actually fun, specially ESL with Mr. Holsten, who helped me so much when I first arrived at Littlebrook. Before I knew it, it was time to come back to Spain. 
I got to meet amazing people from all over the world which I hope to see again sometime in the future.
